title: Lupin the 3rd NORDIC Collection (NO/SV/FI/DK)
description:
Genre: Animation/Anime/Crime/Drama
Age Rating: 11 years & up
Runtime: 424 Minutes
Audio: Japanese (Dolby 2.0 & 5.0)
Subtitles: Norsk, Svenska, Dansk, Suomi



Almost everything released in the scandinavian countries of the Anime series "Lupin the Third". Missing four Finnish Tv-series volumes, as those only contains Finnish subtitles.

Includes:
- Lupin the Third (1971 series) - Episode 1-6
- Lupin the Third - Legend of the Gold of Babylon
- Lupin the Third - Fuma Conspiracy
- Lupin the Third - The Castle of Cagliostro
